I'd also like to announce a paper of which I am a co-author along with
its primary author Joseph Reisinger.  Joe is also in this group, so he
may have his own comments, but the paper is about how we can get reuse
to happen with modules and NEAT-like neuroevolution:

http://nn.cs.utexas.edu/keyword?reisinger:gecco04

Joe also now has the unusual distinction of having published a paper
while still an undergrad!

ken
